ent-type="blocks"><div data-atom-type="desktop-container" class="abGYFbTCX bbGYFbTCX"><div class="abeemc1T3"><div class="bbeemc1T3 cbeemc1T3"><h2 class="abc4Uh03j aboJuLTgt cbc4Uh03j ubc4Uh03j xbc4Uh03j zbc4Uh03j vbc4Uh03j" style="color:#333" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p><b>Почему Росбанк</b></p></h2></div><div class="ebeemc1T3"></div></div></div></div><div style="background:#f1eee8" role="list" data-component-type="blocks"><div data-atom-type="desktop-container" class="abgdQPcpt"><div class="abPBnnAa0 cbPBnnAa0" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:-24px;margin-right:-24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abpBSHjIr DbbpBSHjIr" style="margin-bottom:0;padding:0 24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abhEM9nAq" style="background:#ffffff" role="presentation" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><div class="abQq43rxY" data-test="icon-panel-0" role="listitem"><div class="bbQq43rxY"><div><div class="abHO-HwEI" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:31.25%" aria-hidden="true" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><img class="bbHO-HwEI" src="https://cdn.tbank.ru/static/pages/files/b95337ef-18de-45a2-b752-6cd030fc07f3.svg" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="gbQq43rxY"><h4 class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM fbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Обладаем капиталом более 500&nbsp;млрд рублей</p></h4></div><div class="hbQq43rxY"><div class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM mbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Инвестируем деньги в&nbsp;цифровизацию и&nbsp;запускаем новые сервисы, которые развивают ваш бизнес</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="abpBSHjIr DbbpBSHjIr" style="margin-bottom:0;padding:0 24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abhEM9nAq" style="background:#ffffff" role="presentation" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><div class="abQq43rxY" data-test="icon-panel-1" role="listitem"><div class="bbQq43rxY"><div><div class="abHO-HwEI" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:31.25%" aria-hidden="true" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><img class="bbHO-HwEI" src="https://cdn.tbank.ru/static/pages/files/4680bfe5-e5b9-4cdd-95cf-477fbd22e9ae.svg" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="gbQq43rxY"><h4 class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM fbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Объединяем технологии и&nbsp;сервис</p></h4></div><div class="hbQq43rxY"><div class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM mbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Внедряем инновации, сохраняя живое общение и&nbsp;индивидуальный подход к&nbsp;решению ваших задач</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="background:#f1eee8" role="list" data-component-type="blocks"><div data-atom-type="desktop-container" class="abgdQPcpt"><div class="abPBnnAa0 cbPBnnAa0" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:-24px;margin-right:-24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abpBSHjIr DbbpBSHjIr" style="margin-bottom:0;padding:0 24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abhEM9nAq" style="background:#ffffff" role="presentation" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><div class="abQq43rxY" data-test="icon-panel-0" role="listitem"><div class="bbQq43rxY"><div><div class="abHO-HwEI" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:31.25%" aria-hidden="true" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><img class="bbHO-HwEI" src="https://cdn.tbank.ru/static/pages/files/93dcd4ee-43bd-445f-8eb0-13e2c7c159ad.svg" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="gbQq43rxY"><h4 class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM fbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Обслуживаем более 1,5&nbsp;млн <nobr>бизнес-клиентов</nobr></p></h4></div><div class="hbQq43rxY"><div class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM mbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Среди наших партнеров&nbsp;— Самолет Плюс, Гемотест, СДЭК, Роза Хутор, М.Видео, <nobr>Автодор-Платные</nobr> дороги, S7&nbsp;Airlines</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="abpBSHjIr DbbpBSHjIr" style="margin-bottom:0;padding:0 24px" data-component-type="platform-ui"><div class="abhEM9nAq" style="background:#ffffff" role="presentation" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><div class="abQq43rxY" data-test="icon-panel-1" role="listitem"><div class="bbQq43rxY"><div><div class="abHO-HwEI" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:31.25%" aria-hidden="true" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><img class="bbHO-HwEI" src="https://cdn.tbank.ru/static/pages/files/4680bfe5-e5b9-4cdd-95cf-477fbd22e9ae.svg" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="gbQq43rxY"><h4 class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM fbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Экспертные знания</p></h4></div><div class="hbQq43rxY"><div class="abq_OJ2ma abph8YlNM mbq_OJ2ma vbq_OJ2ma" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><p>Для&nbsp;каждого <nobr>бизнес-сегмента</nobr> назначаем профильных специалистов, которые найдут решения для&nbsp;нестандартных задач</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="background:#f1eee8" role="presentation" data-component-type="blocks"><div data-atom-type="desktop-container" class="ab5BuwAl4"><div class="cbjonROVT"><div class="bbjonROVT"><div class="ab4y3dh6J" data-test="click-area-blue" data-component-type="blocks"><span class="abwhck8P2 bbwhck8P2" data-schema-path="button" data-item-name="Открыть счёт" data-test="htmlTag button" data-component-type="blocks-atom"><button data-active="false" data-component-type="platform-ui" data-test="button" data-size="l" data-appearance="primary" type="button" data-qa-type="tui/button" class="abirFY0QP abBsqEnoB"><span class="bbirFY0QP" style="outline:none" tabindex="-1"><span data-qa-type="tui/button.content-wrapper" class="dbirFY0QP" data-spaced="false"><span data-qa-type="tui/button.content" class="ebirFY0QP fbirFY0QP" data-spaced="false">Открыть счёт</span></span></span></button></span></div></div></div></div></div><footer class="abKNb6G5f" data-component-type="blocks"><div style="background:#F1EEE8" data-component-type="blocks"><div data-atom-type="desktop-container" cl